        {
            "title": "法國評級意外遭標普下調 財長稱此舉無異於雪上加霜",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"646\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/oej.h6iJMDfr4QFIcCou0w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/9cd5b49a76d05cd323ab474683c69db8\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 標普將法國信用評級下調，對該國信譽又一次造成打擊，而當前法國的少數派政府在疲於通過立法應對不斷膨脹的債務負擔。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普意外將法國的評級從AA-下調至A+，稱2026年財政預算草案本周雖已提交議會，但法國政府財政狀況的不確定性依然較高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次降級意味著法國短短一個多月失去了三大信用評級機構中兩家的AA評級，這可能迫使投資標準極其嚴格的一些基金賣出該國債券。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3gfEkaVho1m.lO0FHt8xmA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0NjtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/0c57becad4aa4663dbce6a4cd0ee4286\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普對法國的評級目前與西班牙和葡萄牙持平，比垃圾級高出六檔。穆迪將於10月24日對法國進行下一次評級評估。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9ce7befb-2b9b-3286-b4ff-e2565522f7e5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國最近幾周遭遇了一系列評級挫折，包括惠譽和DBRS對其下調評級，因該國政治長期不穩有可能演變成公共財政危機。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普表示，「如果法國的預算狀況惡化超出我們預期，或者經濟成長前景顯著惡化」，可能會進一步下調法國評級。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：法國總理勒科爾尼挺過兩項不信任動議投票 政治危機迎來喘息之機</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法國財政部長Roland Lescure表示，法國不能忽視不到一年內信用評級第三次被下調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「三家機構已經下調了法國的評級，我們不能忽視這片陰雲，」他周六向Franceinfo表示。「從根本上來說，這無異於雪上加霜，我們要保持清醒和有擔當，對此要嚴肅對待」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題France Gets Debt Alert as S&amp;P Downgrades in Unscheduled Move (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題France’s 3rd Downgrade in Year Is Call to Step Up, Lescure Says</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Kevin Whitelaw.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E9%81%AD%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%8B%E8%AA%BF-%E8%B2%A1%E9%95%B7%E7%A8%B1%E6%AD%A4%E8%88%89%E7%84%A1%E7%95%B0%E6%96%BC%E9%9B%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8A%A0%E9%9C%9C-092529728.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-18 20:10:37",
